articles.title: Video de cámara corporal muestra a ocho policías disparando a Jayland Walker
articles.description: Las autoridades publicaron imágenes de la cámara corporal de la noche en que los policías de Akron, Ohio, le dispararon fatalmente a Jayland Walker. | CNN

articles.title: Polls find high amount of White men think US government is rigged - CNN Video
articles.description: The vast majority of Americans across party lines are unhappy with the state of the US. A new set of polling finds conservatives are among the largest group who believe government is rigged.
